WEBVTT

00:01:15.700 --> 00:01:20.940
=About Love=

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:23.940
=Episode 15=

00:01:24.920 --> 00:01:26.350
Your ex-girlfriend's name is Zhen?

00:01:29.790 --> 00:01:31.070
Zhen Guan and Zhen...

00:01:32.120 --> 00:01:33.150
what's the relationship?

00:01:36.350 --> 00:01:37.400
Who told you that?

00:01:48.430 --> 00:01:49.350
Zhen Guan

00:01:49.840 --> 00:01:51.310
was founded by me and Zhen together.

00:01:52.760 --> 00:01:54.200
When we just graduated from college,

00:01:54.720 --> 00:01:56.120
Zhen was really into studying bags.

00:01:56.430 --> 00:01:57.270
Hey.

00:01:57.760 --> 00:01:58.710
Look at this bag.

00:01:59.710 --> 00:02:01.710
It's definitely one of the eternal classics.

00:02:02.310 --> 00:02:04.070
Too bad they've stopped production now.

00:02:06.760 --> 00:02:08.150
So these vintage bags

00:02:08.360 --> 00:02:10.400
have been around for more than 10 years.

00:02:10.840 --> 00:02:12.080
Would buyers mind that?

00:02:12.480 --> 00:02:13.750
Actually, it has plenty of perks.

00:02:14.590 --> 00:02:16.870
See, most vintage bags

00:02:16.870 --> 00:02:18.310
are limited editions.

00:02:18.710 --> 00:02:20.150
You won't bump into the same one.

00:02:20.360 --> 00:02:22.710
They're unique and never go out of style.

00:02:23.190 --> 00:02:25.520
The price is way lower than new ones.

00:02:26.150 --> 00:02:27.000
Trust me on this.

00:02:27.360 --> 00:02:30.190
Vintage bags only get more valuable.

00:02:31.280 --> 00:02:33.840
I thought the vintage market's potential too.

00:02:34.750 --> 00:02:36.240
So we started Zhen Guan together.

00:02:37.400 --> 00:02:38.870
It went really smoothly at first.

00:02:39.400 --> 00:02:41.310
We bought fast and sold fast.

00:02:41.480 --> 00:02:42.560
You like this wedding dress?

00:02:44.360 --> 00:02:45.280
What are you thinking?

00:02:45.910 --> 00:02:48.000
I just want you to check out this shop.

00:02:48.960 --> 00:02:49.830
Look here.

00:02:49.870 --> 00:02:50.710
Don't you think

00:02:50.910 --> 00:02:53.190
this location and layout are perfect?

00:02:54.590 --> 00:02:56.030
When we've got the money one day,

00:02:56.030 --> 00:02:57.470
we could open our store right here.

00:02:59.000 --> 00:02:59.840
Look.

00:02:59.960 --> 00:03:01.430
There's a busy street right outside.

00:03:01.840 --> 00:03:03.080
We'll make a sign

00:03:03.080 --> 00:03:04.560
even bigger than this one.

00:03:04.800 --> 00:03:05.800
Zhen Guan.

00:03:06.080 --> 00:03:07.080
Visible from far away.

00:03:07.840 --> 00:03:08.750
It's nice, sure.

00:03:09.750 --> 00:03:11.960
But our business is just starting out.

00:03:12.150 --> 00:03:13.190
I haven't thought that far.

00:03:13.400 --> 00:03:15.120
That day will definitely come.

00:03:16.910 --> 00:03:18.030
I believe in you.

00:03:18.470 --> 00:03:19.360
Whatever you do,

00:03:19.710 --> 00:03:20.910
you'll make it work.

00:03:21.840 --> 00:03:23.240
I told you what happened later.

00:03:23.800 --> 00:03:25.030
We got a batch of fake bags.

00:03:25.360 --> 00:03:26.590
Lost everything to a scam.

00:03:26.750 --> 00:03:28.520
- How is it?
- Come on, take a look.

00:03:28.560 --> 00:03:30.120
This bag is fake!

00:03:30.300 --> 00:03:31.240
No way. It can't be.

00:03:31.240 --> 00:03:32.430
Maybe you're misunderstanding.

00:03:32.430 --> 00:03:33.710
How could they sell fakes here?

00:03:33.960 --> 00:03:34.800
Hey, hey.

00:03:35.000 --> 00:03:36.240
You've got quite a crowd here.

00:03:36.430 --> 00:03:37.750
Come on, everyone, take a look.

00:03:37.870 --> 00:03:40.030
Fake bags. Want to buy it or not?

00:03:41.870 --> 00:03:42.750
Let me tell you,

00:03:42.870 --> 00:03:43.750
you have to refund me.

00:03:43.840 --> 00:03:45.080
And I'll get someone to sue you!

00:03:45.560 --> 00:03:47.520
Charging authentic prices for fake bags...

00:03:47.630 --> 00:03:48.710
You've got some nerve, huh?

00:03:49.960 --> 00:03:50.800
She

00:03:53.080 --> 00:03:54.430
left me around that time too.

00:03:54.850 --> 00:03:56.050
Got together with someone else.

00:03:57.190 --> 00:03:59.560
Right then, I got my study abroad offer.

00:04:01.150 --> 00:04:01.990
So I left too.

00:04:05.430 --> 00:04:06.910
My story's pretty lousy, isn't it?

00:04:07.120 --> 00:04:08.360
Not as exciting as you imagined.

00:04:19.260 --> 00:04:21.100
(Shop For Lease)

00:04:21.120 --> 00:04:22.950
After coming back, I kept doing appraisals.

00:04:24.870 --> 00:04:26.750
Part of the reason I keep doing this job

00:04:27.310 --> 00:04:28.750
is because I don't want others to be

00:04:28.750 --> 00:04:29.600
scammed like I was.

00:04:31.160 --> 00:04:32.430
I reopened Zhen Guan.

00:04:33.060 --> 00:04:34.020
(Shop For Lease)

00:04:34.040 --> 00:04:36.180
It's kind of making up for what I lost.

00:04:36.180 --> 00:04:38.140
(Shop For Lease)

00:04:38.510 --> 00:04:39.510
I admit it.

00:04:41.270 --> 00:04:42.830
I learned appraisal for Zhen.

00:04:44.800 --> 00:04:45.750
But I want to tell you,

00:04:46.120 --> 00:04:47.270
she and I are over.

00:04:48.120 --> 00:04:50.190
If the name Zhen Guan bothers you,

00:04:50.580 --> 00:04:52.390
- I can get it changed...
- It doesn't matter.

00:04:53.600 --> 00:04:55.240
Honestly, I wanted to be more carefree.

00:04:56.800 --> 00:04:59.240
But when I first heard her name, I realized,

00:05:02.720 --> 00:05:03.950
I'm just an ordinary person.

00:05:06.270 --> 00:05:07.680
We're all ordinary people.

00:05:09.360 --> 00:05:10.200
Same here.

00:05:14.450 --> 00:05:15.720
About that question I asked you,

00:05:15.720 --> 00:05:16.650
what do you have to say?

00:05:18.070 --> 00:05:19.920
Why did I have someone test you?

00:05:25.070 --> 00:05:25.920
Do you remember?

00:05:25.930 --> 00:05:27.560
You once told me about a little boy

00:05:27.560 --> 00:05:29.190
whose dad cheated on his mom.

00:05:32.120 --> 00:05:33.240
And you asked me then.

00:05:34.000 --> 00:05:35.160
You asked me what I'd choose.

00:05:41.630 --> 00:05:43.190
I was really young then.

00:05:45.680 --> 00:05:47.270
I told my mom without even thinking.

00:05:50.120 --> 00:05:52.190
Silly, you must have seen wrong.

00:05:52.750 --> 00:05:55.360
You're the only child we have.

00:05:56.000 --> 00:05:56.840
Good girl.

00:05:56.930 --> 00:05:57.780
Mm.

00:05:57.800 --> 00:05:58.720
Stop crying.

00:05:59.240 --> 00:06:00.430
I've always wanted to believe.

00:06:01.720 --> 00:06:03.830
But whenever Dad went on a trip, that scene...

00:06:06.430 --> 00:06:08.270
That scene would flash in my mind.

00:06:09.310 --> 00:06:12.240
Xiaoxi, listen to Mom while I'm away.

00:06:12.750 --> 00:06:14.040
I'm leaving now.

00:06:14.920 --> 00:06:17.920
Dad, when will you be back?

00:06:18.430 --> 00:06:20.950
Dad will be back the day after tomorrow.

00:06:21.920 --> 00:06:24.680
Xiaoxi, tell me,

00:06:25.920 --> 00:06:27.680
what gift do you want?

00:06:27.950 --> 00:06:31.040
I don't want gifts, just come home soon.

00:06:40.480 --> 00:06:42.160
Has Mom been fooled all along?

00:06:43.720 --> 00:06:45.560
That doubt kept eating away at me.

00:06:52.560 --> 00:06:54.390
I later got into university there.

00:06:56.390 --> 00:06:58.430
I even hired someone to follow my dad.

00:07:00.720 --> 00:07:02.040
But I didn't find anything.

00:07:04.390 --> 00:07:06.510
The image of my dad holding that girl

00:07:08.950 --> 00:07:10.800
felt like a nightmare from my childhood.

00:07:14.270 --> 00:07:16.390
Later, in relationships, I often encountered

00:07:16.600 --> 00:07:17.950
lies and deception.

00:07:18.360 --> 00:07:19.680
I like you, I...

00:07:19.780 --> 00:07:20.800
When I first saw you, I...

00:07:20.800 --> 00:07:21.950
I just fell for you.

00:07:22.430 --> 00:07:23.750
I have two movie tickets.

00:07:25.560 --> 00:07:27.310
I know suspicion is like a swamp.

00:07:27.560 --> 00:07:29.430
Getting stuck in it is so painful.

00:07:31.240 --> 00:07:33.120
So I started to identify for them...

00:07:33.920 --> 00:07:35.070
What's genuine feeling?

00:07:35.920 --> 00:07:36.760
What's deception?

00:07:41.240 --> 00:07:42.360
Some people believe tests

00:07:42.360 --> 00:07:44.480
can measure loyalty in love.

00:07:44.630 --> 00:07:45.470
Do you know?

00:07:50.310 --> 00:07:53.430
♪I think of you, always loving you♪

00:07:53.750 --> 00:07:56.870
♪Always meeting you in my dreams♪

00:07:57.310 --> 00:08:00.390
♪Falling for this sweet feeling♪

00:08:00.560 --> 00:08:04.680
♪From today on, you're the only one♪

00:08:05.000 --> 00:08:08.120
♪The only one♪

00:08:08.310 --> 00:08:10.510
Alright.

00:08:13.120 --> 00:08:14.950
Come on, buddy!

00:08:15.040 --> 00:08:15.880
Mr. Cao.

00:08:16.240 --> 00:08:17.360
Hey, Sen.

00:08:18.040 --> 00:08:18.880
Hey.

00:08:20.190 --> 00:08:22.270
That proposal your team did this time

00:08:22.680 --> 00:08:25.390
really took me by surprise...in the best way.

00:08:25.550 --> 00:08:26.600
I just can't figure it out

00:08:26.600 --> 00:08:29.360
how you came up with such brilliant ideas.

00:08:29.600 --> 00:08:30.560
Mr. Cao, you flatter me.

00:08:30.870 --> 00:08:31.830
It was all

00:08:32.270 --> 00:08:33.150
team effort.

00:08:33.220 --> 00:08:34.360
Everyone pooling their ideas.

00:08:34.910 --> 00:08:36.080
Here, Mr. Cao, I toast to you.

00:08:36.120 --> 00:08:37.360
No, no, I should toast you.

00:08:37.840 --> 00:08:38.720
I'll say it again.

00:08:39.510 --> 00:08:41.240
You've got a bright future ahead.

00:08:41.360 --> 00:08:42.870
- Okay.
- Thanks.

00:08:47.720 --> 00:08:48.750
Honestly speaking,

00:08:49.320 --> 00:08:50.790
do you actually have a girlfriend?

00:08:51.370 --> 00:08:52.230
Yeah.

00:08:52.230 --> 00:08:53.080
You serious?

00:08:53.200 --> 00:08:54.040
Totally.

00:08:54.200 --> 00:08:55.040
Oh no.

00:08:55.550 --> 00:08:56.390
Oh no, oh no.

00:08:57.030 --> 00:08:57.870
What's the deal?

00:08:58.670 --> 00:08:59.630
- Mr. Cao...
- Rou!

00:08:59.630 --> 00:09:00.550
Hey.

00:09:01.790 --> 00:09:02.630
What do you mean?

00:09:03.630 --> 00:09:05.240
Are you trying to set me up?

00:09:06.030 --> 00:09:08.750
Our company's Business Manager. Come.

00:09:10.390 --> 00:09:11.390
Guys,

00:09:11.750 --> 00:09:14.390
show of hands if you agree Rou's our Goddess.

00:09:15.440 --> 00:09:16.280
Agreed!

00:09:17.840 --> 00:09:19.440
The dashing Director Sen

00:09:19.720 --> 00:09:21.870
and the stunning Miss Rou.

00:09:22.240 --> 00:09:23.750
What kind of pair are these two?

00:09:23.900 --> 00:09:24.750
A match made in chaos.

00:09:24.750 --> 00:09:25.790
Nonsense!

00:09:27.150 --> 00:09:28.720
More like a perfect match!

00:09:29.120 --> 00:09:30.270
But it's a pity now.

00:09:31.320 --> 00:09:33.240
Mr. Cao, I'm not that lucky.

00:09:33.670 --> 00:09:36.200
Director Sen mentioned he had a girlfriend.

00:09:36.480 --> 00:09:38.670
They've been together quite a while, right?

00:09:39.720 --> 00:09:40.580
Yeah.

00:09:40.600 --> 00:09:42.510
You've never changed girlfriends?

00:09:43.120 --> 00:09:44.320
No, still the same one.

00:09:44.670 --> 00:09:47.630
Wow, Director Sen's really devoted.

00:09:47.870 --> 00:09:48.750
Alright, cut it out.

00:09:48.960 --> 00:09:49.880
How about one day,

00:09:49.880 --> 00:09:52.080
we invite Sen's girlfriend to join us?

00:09:52.270 --> 00:09:53.300
I'd really like to see,

00:09:53.320 --> 00:09:55.270
what kind of girl has that charm

00:09:55.390 --> 00:09:56.870
to win over our Director Sen.

00:09:56.910 --> 00:09:57.840
- Good.
- Good.

00:09:57.840 --> 00:09:58.690
Right?

00:09:58.700 --> 00:09:59.560
Next time for sure.

00:09:59.670 --> 00:10:00.600
Absolutely, Mr. Cao.

00:10:01.030 --> 00:10:02.150
Mr. Cao, this is our song.

00:10:02.270 --> 00:10:03.840
Let's see.

00:10:03.870 --> 00:10:05.150
Alright, it's my turn.

00:10:05.440 --> 00:10:06.280
Come on.

00:10:07.720 --> 00:10:10.150
♪We row the boat together♪

00:10:10.150 --> 00:10:12.750
♪Picking red water chestnuts♪

00:10:12.750 --> 00:10:13.750
Applause!

00:10:13.750 --> 00:10:16.120
♪He's got the heart full of care♪

00:10:16.120 --> 00:10:18.870
♪She's got the heart that dares♪

00:10:19.510 --> 00:10:21.470
♪Just like two corners of a chestnut♪

00:10:21.960 --> 00:10:23.870
♪We're born from the same root♪

00:10:23.870 --> 00:10:26.080
♪Our hearts beat as one♪

00:10:27.150 --> 00:10:29.600
♪We row the boat together♪

00:10:29.600 --> 00:10:32.240
♪Picking red water chestnuts♪

00:10:36.760 --> 00:10:37.610
Together, let's toast!

00:10:37.630 --> 00:10:39.150
Come on, come on!

00:10:40.320 --> 00:10:41.790
Director Sen, this toast is to you.

00:10:41.910 --> 00:10:43.080
They started having fun.

00:10:48.670 --> 00:10:50.000
You probably don't remember me.

00:10:50.390 --> 00:10:51.750
We've met three times before.

00:10:54.510 --> 00:10:55.960
Last time you sang a song,

00:10:56.030 --> 00:10:58.030
you were still as happy as a kid.

00:10:58.440 --> 00:11:00.870
This time you're like an adult. What's up?

00:11:01.630 --> 00:11:03.440
Are adults never happy?

00:11:04.360 --> 00:11:05.670
Is it about your love life?

00:11:06.480 --> 00:11:07.440
You can tell?

00:11:08.270 --> 00:11:09.510
I heard it in your voice.

00:11:10.200 --> 00:11:11.720
You almost sang yourself to tears.

00:11:16.120 --> 00:11:17.030
Broke up?

00:11:19.240 --> 00:11:20.080
Nope.

00:11:29.200 --> 00:11:30.240
Ever been in love?

00:11:30.320 --> 00:11:31.550
What do you think?

00:11:32.360 --> 00:11:33.200
How many times?

00:11:34.440 --> 00:11:35.630
It's too noisy here.

00:11:36.030 --> 00:11:37.270
Let's talk somewhere else.

00:11:38.670 --> 00:11:39.550
Impressed?

00:11:39.630 --> 00:11:41.200
Yeah, very.

00:11:41.870 --> 00:11:44.440
This was my past love life.

00:11:47.000 --> 00:11:48.630
I never gave my whole heart.

00:11:50.960 --> 00:11:52.720
Probably my childhood experiences

00:11:52.720 --> 00:11:54.320
left me so insecure.

00:11:55.670 --> 00:11:59.080
The only way

00:12:00.000 --> 00:12:01.600
I could trust someone in love

00:12:01.960 --> 00:12:02.870
was to test

00:12:03.450 --> 00:12:04.320
if you'd fall

00:12:04.320 --> 00:12:05.840
for another girl too.

00:12:11.960 --> 00:12:12.800
I'm sorry.

00:12:15.960 --> 00:12:17.440
All the girls who tested me

00:12:18.790 --> 00:12:20.000
were your friends?

00:12:21.080 --> 00:12:21.960
That's why

00:12:23.440 --> 00:12:25.360
you never introduced your friends to me.

00:12:26.840 --> 00:12:27.720
No.

00:12:28.840 --> 00:12:31.440
Only the one pretending to be
a housekeeper is my friend.

00:12:32.480 --> 00:12:33.480
Her name's Yingtao.

00:12:34.870 --> 00:12:36.840
I wanted to introduce you,

00:12:38.720 --> 00:12:40.030
but I was scared you'd mind.

00:12:52.360 --> 00:12:53.200
So,

00:12:55.510 --> 00:12:56.480
Jiang Yifan,

00:12:59.720 --> 00:13:00.630
is that you?

00:13:23.790 --> 00:13:24.630
Yes.

00:13:29.480 --> 00:13:31.630
You could say Jiang Yifan has absolutely

00:13:31.790 --> 00:13:33.080
no sense of guilt or shame.

00:13:33.510 --> 00:13:35.720
She really is a detestable, wicked woman.

00:13:36.320 --> 00:13:38.550
I am that wicked woman, Jiang Yifan.

00:13:41.480 --> 00:13:42.720
Are you wondering...

00:13:44.320 --> 00:13:46.510
Was my meeting with Gong a coincidence?

00:13:46.750 --> 00:13:47.590
No.

00:13:49.270 --> 00:13:50.270
I arranged to meet him.

00:13:52.240 --> 00:13:54.150
Every time we talked, the topic was you.

00:13:54.480 --> 00:13:55.720
Honestly, I feel like Bei and I

00:13:55.840 --> 00:13:57.670
were meant to end up together.

00:13:57.870 --> 00:14:00.080
He's like another version of me in the world.

00:14:00.240 --> 00:14:01.670
I hope that one day I can

00:14:02.360 --> 00:14:03.910
tell him everything about myself.

00:14:04.120 --> 00:14:05.790
I've been watching over you for him,

00:14:06.000 --> 00:14:08.150
making sure you're delivered to him safely.

00:14:08.670 --> 00:14:09.550
So,

00:14:10.440 --> 00:14:12.030
you have his contact information?

00:14:15.120 --> 00:14:15.960
Yes.

00:14:22.840 --> 00:14:26.120
When you were doing your tests,

00:14:27.320 --> 00:14:28.870
did you ever get...

00:14:29.080 --> 00:14:29.960
No.

00:14:31.120 --> 00:14:33.080
Once I get the audio evidence, I stop.

00:14:40.240 --> 00:14:41.080
My turn to ask.

00:14:49.750 --> 00:14:51.030
Last Saturday night,

00:14:51.900 --> 00:14:53.030
after the dinner gathering...

00:14:53.150 --> 00:14:54.910
I even invited him over for drinks last week.

00:14:55.150 --> 00:14:56.550
Did you go to An Miu's place?

00:14:57.120 --> 00:14:58.360
Alright, I got it.

00:14:58.480 --> 00:14:59.390
Go shower first.

00:15:03.870 --> 00:15:04.710
Yes.

00:15:05.730 --> 00:15:06.970
She suddenly called me that day,

00:15:07.000 --> 00:15:08.390
told me she was back.

00:15:09.550 --> 00:15:10.630
I went over that night.

00:15:11.390 --> 00:15:12.320
Why didn't you tell me?

00:15:13.600 --> 00:15:15.320
When we were at the dinner gathering,

00:15:15.390 --> 00:15:16.600
she suddenly said she was back.

00:15:17.860 --> 00:15:19.130
I was afraid you'd misunderstand.

00:15:19.720 --> 00:15:20.560
So,

00:15:21.440 --> 00:15:22.360
I planned to settle her

00:15:22.670 --> 00:15:23.960
and then tell you the next day.

00:15:25.960 --> 00:15:27.750
But that night when I went over,

00:15:32.510 --> 00:15:34.600
she suddenly confessed to me.

00:15:36.000 --> 00:15:37.470
Of course, I rejected her on the spot.

00:15:39.120 --> 00:15:40.600
When I got back, I realized

00:15:41.790 --> 00:15:43.360
things had gotten a bit messy.

00:15:43.960 --> 00:15:44.840
So I didn't tell you.

00:15:45.510 --> 00:15:46.360
I thought,

00:15:47.320 --> 00:15:48.630
maybe I could introduce you two

00:15:49.550 --> 00:15:50.630
and let you become friends.

00:15:51.870 --> 00:15:52.710
That way,

00:15:53.670 --> 00:15:55.000
she'd finally give up on me.

00:15:56.700 --> 00:15:57.670
You care about her a lot?

00:15:58.670 --> 00:15:59.910
I wouldn't say care, really.

00:16:01.960 --> 00:16:02.800
She's...

00:16:03.910 --> 00:16:05.320
She's a friend, I guess.

00:16:27.200 --> 00:16:29.000
I think we both...

00:16:31.120 --> 00:16:32.440
need some space to cool off.

00:16:39.000 --> 00:16:40.200
Let's take a break for a while.

00:16:42.360 --> 00:16:43.200
Think things through.

00:16:53.030 --> 00:16:54.200
What were you asking me

00:16:54.200 --> 00:16:55.480
earlier in the private room?

00:16:57.200 --> 00:16:58.040
Ah?

00:16:59.320 --> 00:17:00.240
Oh, nothing.

00:17:01.440 --> 00:17:02.630
Just asking casually.

00:17:03.920 --> 00:17:04.770
Oh.

00:17:04.790 --> 00:17:05.790
I remember now.

00:17:06.230 --> 00:17:07.580
I've been in lots of relationships.

00:17:07.680 --> 00:17:08.520
But,

00:17:08.720 --> 00:17:09.560
I'm single now.

00:17:10.160 --> 00:17:11.000
Then let me ask you.

00:17:11.880 --> 00:17:13.400
After so many experiences in love,

00:17:14.790 --> 00:17:15.720
do you ever feel numb?

00:17:16.310 --> 00:17:17.150
Or maybe,

00:17:17.270 --> 00:17:18.720
like it's lost that spark?

00:17:19.400 --> 00:17:20.350
Like no more feelings?

00:17:21.110 --> 00:17:23.550
If you see love as something that wears out

00:17:23.700 --> 00:17:24.900
and fades away a bit each time,

00:17:25.270 --> 00:17:27.480
it makes sense that you feel so numb

00:17:27.590 --> 00:17:28.920
and incapable of loving

00:17:29.680 --> 00:17:30.880
someone else.

00:17:31.880 --> 00:17:32.720
But

00:17:33.600 --> 00:17:35.070
it sounds more like an excuse when

00:17:35.200 --> 00:17:37.270
you haven't met or can't have true love.

00:17:40.110 --> 00:17:42.030
Do you still stay in touch with your exes?

00:17:42.640 --> 00:17:44.920
Some get blocked, never talking again.

00:17:45.720 --> 00:17:46.560
Thanks.

00:17:46.720 --> 00:17:47.750
Some stay friends.

00:17:48.720 --> 00:17:49.560
So basically,

00:17:49.590 --> 00:17:51.030
you start dating a new boyfriend,

00:17:51.160 --> 00:17:53.680
but still keep contact with your ex, right?

00:17:54.030 --> 00:17:55.000
Of course.

00:17:55.400 --> 00:17:56.750
I can't wipe my social circle clean

00:17:56.830 --> 00:17:58.310
every time I fall in love.

00:17:58.440 --> 00:17:59.350
Even hang out together?

00:18:00.200 --> 00:18:02.640
Why are you so hung up on this ex thing?

00:18:03.270 --> 00:18:05.750
If you went out with your ex for a date,

00:18:06.200 --> 00:18:07.270
should I thoughtfully

00:18:07.350 --> 00:18:08.880
send you to see your ex,

00:18:09.070 --> 00:18:10.720
smile warmly, then tell you,

00:18:10.880 --> 00:18:12.030
"Have a good time"?

00:18:12.640 --> 00:18:14.240
Is that how a normal guy should do?

00:18:18.160 --> 00:18:19.270
Well, I can't do that.

00:18:20.200 --> 00:18:21.220
I'm not that broad-minded.

00:18:22.640 --> 00:18:23.960
It's not that I have dirty ideas,

00:18:24.270 --> 00:18:25.350
judging your character.

00:18:25.880 --> 00:18:27.510
It's that I have no reason to trust him.

00:18:32.110 --> 00:18:33.270
I don't feel secure about it.

00:18:35.070 --> 00:18:36.720
I want you to consider my feelings

00:18:36.920 --> 00:18:37.830
and draw the line.

00:18:38.720 --> 00:18:40.680
I'm scared every time you two meet,

00:18:40.920 --> 00:18:41.790
every ambiguous chat

00:18:42.000 --> 00:18:43.240
might let him push further.

00:18:43.830 --> 00:18:45.510
I'm scared you'll bring up the past,

00:18:45.720 --> 00:18:46.560
and as you talk,

00:18:46.800 --> 00:18:47.830
things might lose control.

00:18:48.110 --> 00:18:49.750
Then I'd end up looking like a fool,

00:18:50.160 --> 00:18:52.030
tangled up and overthinking everything.

00:18:52.160 --> 00:18:53.310
I'm not a normal person.

00:18:53.590 --> 00:18:54.680
What did I do wrong?

00:18:55.750 --> 00:18:56.680
What's wrong with me?

00:18:57.790 --> 00:18:58.950
What exactly is wrong with me?

00:19:11.510 --> 00:19:12.590
Let me ask you something.

00:19:13.240 --> 00:19:14.080
Mm.

00:19:14.480 --> 00:19:15.590
Who do you think

00:19:16.200 --> 00:19:17.550
would be more likely to cheat

00:19:18.640 --> 00:19:19.920
if we got together?

00:19:23.270 --> 00:19:24.720
Don't be shy. Just answer.

00:19:24.750 --> 00:19:26.270
- It's fine, I'm...
- You.

00:19:29.480 --> 00:19:30.440
Then why don't you think

00:19:30.510 --> 00:19:32.270
our chances would be about the same?

00:19:32.750 --> 00:19:33.750
You're being too modest.

00:19:34.790 --> 00:19:36.110
Alright, hang on.

00:19:37.720 --> 00:19:38.790
Excuse me, waiter.

00:19:39.830 --> 00:19:40.790
Do you have any coins?

00:19:40.790 --> 00:19:41.630
Oh, yes.

00:19:42.030 --> 00:19:42.880
Could you give me one?

00:19:44.400 --> 00:19:45.240
Thanks.

00:19:50.830 --> 00:19:51.670
Take a guess.

00:19:53.510 --> 00:19:54.350
Tails.

00:19:55.310 --> 00:19:56.160
Wrong.

00:19:56.510 --> 00:19:57.440
Let me ask you again.

00:19:58.440 --> 00:19:59.440
If

00:20:00.640 --> 00:20:03.200
I flip 100 times and it's always heads,

00:20:03.960 --> 00:20:05.680
what's the chance on the 101th flip?

00:20:06.270 --> 00:20:07.110
Still heads.

00:20:07.350 --> 00:20:08.310
Wrong again.

00:20:09.160 --> 00:20:11.750
No matter what the odds were before,

00:20:12.880 --> 00:20:14.310
the next flip's probability

00:20:14.750 --> 00:20:16.400
is always 50%.

00:20:17.590 --> 00:20:19.590
We each have a 50% chance

00:20:19.720 --> 00:20:20.750
of betraying the other.

00:20:22.070 --> 00:20:23.010
So how can we expect

00:20:23.020 --> 00:20:24.790
100% sense of security?

00:20:25.440 --> 00:20:27.240
If someone's sense of security

00:20:27.590 --> 00:20:29.270
completely depends on others,

00:20:30.160 --> 00:20:31.960
they'll always feel insecure.

00:20:33.960 --> 00:20:34.800
Thanks.

00:20:35.310 --> 00:20:37.000
Hey, babe. Where are you now?

00:20:37.640 --> 00:20:38.590
Let's pick another spot.

00:20:39.440 --> 00:20:40.480
Isn't that your colleague?

00:20:40.550 --> 00:20:42.590
He's also an ex I want to block.

00:20:47.720 --> 00:20:49.030
Wow, you've got plenty of exes.

00:20:58.110 --> 00:21:00.110
Didn't know karaoke had places like this.

00:21:00.790 --> 00:21:02.830
Totally different from the other room.

00:21:03.510 --> 00:21:04.720
The decor style here...

00:21:04.750 --> 00:21:05.790
This place is nice, right?

00:21:06.160 --> 00:21:07.310
- Ah.
- And it's quiet.

00:21:07.800 --> 00:21:08.920
No one's around to bother us.

00:21:09.880 --> 00:21:10.720
Oh.

00:21:14.680 --> 00:21:16.790
Whoa, we can watch movies here too.

00:21:19.190 --> 00:21:20.710
We just walked right in.

00:21:20.750 --> 00:21:21.720
Is that really okay?

00:21:22.680 --> 00:21:24.160
Our company comes here a lot.

00:21:24.400 --> 00:21:25.750
I'm usually the one hosting guests.

00:21:26.350 --> 00:21:27.510
So I get certain perks.

00:21:27.550 --> 00:21:28.390
Oh.

00:21:29.480 --> 00:21:30.320
Come on, sit down.

00:21:43.440 --> 00:21:44.640
Do you think

00:21:45.270 --> 00:21:47.400
you love your girlfriend more,

00:21:48.030 --> 00:21:49.680
or she loves you more?

00:21:51.030 --> 00:21:52.110
Why do you ask?

00:21:54.240 --> 00:21:55.310
Love itself

00:21:55.640 --> 00:21:57.590
is an unsolvable equation.

00:21:58.160 --> 00:21:59.110
No probability.

00:21:59.510 --> 00:22:00.480
No measures.

00:22:02.350 --> 00:22:03.830
If you insist on solving it,

00:22:04.440 --> 00:22:05.960
you're just torturing yourself.

00:22:06.880 --> 00:22:08.160
Knowing you love her

00:22:08.640 --> 00:22:09.480
is enough.

00:22:12.590 --> 00:22:13.510
Give up everything

00:22:14.070 --> 00:22:14.910
just to love?

00:22:16.200 --> 00:22:17.310
Could you move a bit closer?

00:22:32.160 --> 00:22:33.750
I'll answer your earlier question.

00:22:34.750 --> 00:22:35.590
Of course.

00:22:35.920 --> 00:22:37.350
Don't think about anything else.

00:22:40.510 --> 00:22:42.270
Like we're in this room right now.

00:22:43.640 --> 00:22:44.830
No matter what

00:22:46.550 --> 00:22:47.510
we do...

00:22:49.550 --> 00:22:50.720
If she loves you,

00:22:51.310 --> 00:22:52.590
then we did nothing.

00:22:54.000 --> 00:22:55.110
But if she's suspicious,

00:22:55.880 --> 00:22:58.030
even if you walk out of here right now,

00:22:59.030 --> 00:23:00.160
it won't clear your name.

00:23:04.160 --> 00:23:05.920
Seeking the truth in love

00:23:06.550 --> 00:23:08.070
is utterly meaningless.

00:23:09.680 --> 00:23:10.960
There's no real cause and effect.

00:23:12.920 --> 00:23:14.070
Some things

00:23:14.920 --> 00:23:16.400
we simply cannot find.

00:23:19.030 --> 00:23:20.240
And maybe if we do find them,

00:23:21.830 --> 00:23:22.750
they're already gone.

00:23:27.000 --> 00:23:27.840
I really

00:23:29.590 --> 00:23:31.310
wish I could be carefree like you.

00:23:36.000 --> 00:23:37.440
This isn't carefree.

00:23:38.680 --> 00:23:40.920
I just haven't met

00:23:41.030 --> 00:23:42.720
the one who makes me hold on.

00:23:54.110 --> 00:23:54.950
Your name's

00:23:55.640 --> 00:23:56.480
Rou?

00:23:57.400 --> 00:23:58.240
Mm.

00:24:02.750 --> 00:24:03.790
Your name's Sen.

00:24:06.070 --> 00:24:07.510
When I first met you,

00:24:07.680 --> 00:24:08.920
I was sitting right next to you.

00:24:08.920 --> 00:24:09.770
- Impressive.
- Okay.

00:24:09.790 --> 00:24:11.510
Very impressive.

00:24:11.640 --> 00:24:12.590
Good for you.

00:24:12.640 --> 00:24:13.720
Rou.

00:24:13.920 --> 00:24:15.480
What are you waiting for?

00:24:15.590 --> 00:24:17.680
Make a proper toast to Mr. Chen and Mr. Sen.

00:24:17.680 --> 00:24:19.720
- Got it.
- Mr. Chen, we must thank you.

00:24:20.680 --> 00:24:21.880
Let's just drink like this.

00:24:21.880 --> 00:24:22.720
Is that okay?

00:24:22.720 --> 00:24:24.640
- I'm out of wine.
- This is all I've left.

00:24:25.310 --> 00:24:26.150
Pour me some.

00:24:26.240 --> 00:24:27.080
Here.

00:24:27.200 --> 00:24:28.040
Thanks.

00:24:29.590 --> 00:24:31.270
Mr. Chen, I'll finish mine. Enjoy.

00:24:31.280 --> 00:24:32.140
Oh.

00:24:32.140 --> 00:24:33.350
Alright.

00:24:38.880 --> 00:24:39.920
I just remembered.

00:24:40.310 --> 00:24:42.310
That day you toasted everyone at the table,

00:24:42.590 --> 00:24:43.510
remaining calm,

00:24:43.920 --> 00:24:44.920
smiling the whole time.

00:24:45.200 --> 00:24:46.240
Back then I was thinking,

00:24:46.960 --> 00:24:48.750
"This girl looks so fragile,

00:24:49.200 --> 00:24:50.590
but she can really hold her liquor."

00:24:51.350 --> 00:24:52.640
Hold my liquor? Please.

00:24:53.030 --> 00:24:54.550
I secretly puked more than once.

00:24:56.550 --> 00:24:58.310
Feels like I don't know you at all.

00:24:59.310 --> 00:25:00.790
Like I only met you today.

00:25:11.920 --> 00:25:13.160
Do you think

00:25:13.720 --> 00:25:15.160
I'm just an easy kind of girl?

00:25:15.960 --> 00:25:16.920
No, no, not at all.

00:25:16.920 --> 00:25:17.760
Uh…

00:25:19.310 --> 00:25:21.160
I think you're pretty genuine.

00:25:21.440 --> 00:25:22.310
Seriously.

00:25:27.200 --> 00:25:28.960
The second and third time we met,

00:25:30.000 --> 00:25:31.920
I kept wondering that

00:25:32.880 --> 00:25:34.310
maybe you'd already broken up.

00:25:35.400 --> 00:25:36.830
Only found out when we met today

00:25:37.920 --> 00:25:39.240
that you haven't broken up yet.

00:25:40.160 --> 00:25:41.030
But…

00:25:41.750 --> 00:25:43.030
Seems like things aren't great.

00:25:43.830 --> 00:25:44.920
She and I

00:25:45.480 --> 00:25:47.000
actually had a fight tonight.

00:25:47.070 --> 00:25:48.240
You don't need to tell me.

00:25:50.310 --> 00:25:51.680
I chatted with you today

00:25:52.830 --> 00:25:53.960
because I hope you can

00:25:54.270 --> 00:25:55.590
keep being happy in the future.

00:25:58.310 --> 00:25:59.150
Besides,

00:26:00.240 --> 00:26:01.680
I'm leaving my job this month.

00:26:03.030 --> 00:26:04.030
I didn't expect

00:26:04.400 --> 00:26:06.350
to see you again before I go,

00:26:07.640 --> 00:26:09.400
and still get to talk like this.

00:26:11.550 --> 00:26:12.640
I guess I'm lucky.

00:26:13.070 --> 00:26:14.720
Wait… are you changing jobs?

00:26:15.000 --> 00:26:16.030
I haven't decided yet.

00:26:17.400 --> 00:26:18.510
Maybe…

00:26:19.380 --> 00:26:20.400
I'll move to another city.

00:26:21.920 --> 00:26:23.310
So… will you be coming back?

00:26:30.300 --> 00:26:32.890
♪I'll admit♪

00:26:32.900 --> 00:26:36.930
♪My back is faced against the wall♪

00:26:38.510 --> 00:26:39.750
Do you want me to come back?

00:26:41.340 --> 00:26:45.890
♪For this feeling to have you♪

00:26:46.180 --> 00:26:49.660
♪I'll resist your gaze♪

00:26:49.660 --> 00:26:52.890
♪Your lips, your touches again♪

00:26:53.780 --> 00:26:57.130
♪There's no one
that I wouldn't try to fool♪

00:26:57.140 --> 00:27:00.810
♪For an image of you♪

00:27:02.100 --> 00:27:04.250
♪Take my hand again♪

00:27:04.260 --> 00:27:06.010
♪Take my mind again♪

00:27:06.100 --> 00:27:09.450
♪Break into my heart again♪

00:27:09.860 --> 00:27:11.770
♪I'm falling out again♪

00:27:11.780 --> 00:27:13.890
♪I'm on my knees again♪

00:27:13.900 --> 00:27:17.500
♪To beg for the truth♪

00:27:17.500 --> 00:27:21.180
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

00:27:22.170 --> 00:27:23.480
There are dumplings in the fridge.

00:27:25.500 --> 00:27:26.480
Eat it if you get hungry.

00:27:26.870 --> 00:27:29.970
♪I thought it had came from below us♪

00:27:30.000 --> 00:27:33.090
♪Did it come from above?♪

00:27:33.110 --> 00:27:37.010
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

00:27:37.210 --> 00:27:42.170
♪Is it a push or a shove?♪

00:27:42.710 --> 00:27:44.890
♪Is it violent or warming, entrancing♪

00:27:44.900 --> 00:27:48.810
♪This secret of love♪

00:27:49.740 --> 00:27:51.170
♪I'm addicted♪

00:27:51.860 --> 00:27:55.220
♪Every second of the day♪

00:27:57.180 --> 00:28:00.660
♪Walking round the corners
of the room♪

00:28:01.060 --> 00:28:04.980
♪Chasing your shadows♪

00:28:04.980 --> 00:28:07.060
♪When the curtains close♪

00:28:07.060 --> 00:28:09.100
♪I'll still be loving you♪

00:28:09.100 --> 00:28:12.260
♪Sinking deep and deeper again♪

00:28:13.020 --> 00:28:14.940
♪When the oceans fall♪

00:28:14.940 --> 00:28:16.780
♪I'll still be holding you♪

00:28:16.780 --> 00:28:20.460
♪Cause you are my truth♪

00:28:20.500 --> 00:28:24.540
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

00:28:24.540 --> 00:28:29.300
♪Is that the secret to love?♪

00:28:29.900 --> 00:28:33.020
♪I thought it had came from below us♪

00:28:33.020 --> 00:28:36.500
♪Did it come from above?♪

00:28:36.500 --> 00:28:40.340
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

00:28:40.340 --> 00:28:45.500
♪Is it a push or a shove?♪

00:28:45.740 --> 00:28:48.020
♪Is it violent or warming, entrancing♪

00:28:48.040 --> 00:28:53.290
♪This secret of love♪

00:28:54.380 --> 00:28:57.880
♪There's no more reason
to fight it♪

00:28:58.400 --> 00:29:02.080
♪There's no more reason
to lie again♪

00:29:02.500 --> 00:29:09.210
♪There's no more reason
to run away and hide♪

00:29:37.930 --> 00:29:38.770
Mm.

00:29:38.790 --> 00:29:40.270
Have you eaten? Want me...

00:29:40.640 --> 00:29:41.790
to heat it up for you?

00:29:42.590 --> 00:29:43.430
I...

00:29:43.880 --> 00:29:44.720
Uh...

00:29:45.510 --> 00:29:46.590
It's fine for now.

00:29:49.510 --> 00:29:50.350
Mm.

00:30:06.830 --> 00:30:07.680
Sit down.

00:30:12.550 --> 00:30:13.390
I'm sorry.

00:30:15.640 --> 00:30:17.160
I shouldn't have snapped at you,

00:30:18.070 --> 00:30:19.440
and shouldn't have thrown things.

00:30:20.640 --> 00:30:21.590
I apologize to you.

00:30:25.480 --> 00:30:27.110
You're acting like a child.

00:30:41.160 --> 00:30:43.160
Back when you were still with Lun,

00:30:43.880 --> 00:30:45.070
I already liked you.

00:30:46.880 --> 00:30:47.960
Back then I just hoped

00:30:47.960 --> 00:30:49.640
you'd turn around and notice me.

00:30:50.790 --> 00:30:52.000
But we're already together.

00:30:52.510 --> 00:30:53.640
Even so, I'm still scared.

00:30:54.400 --> 00:30:56.070
Scared you'd think I wasn't as good as him.

00:30:58.230 --> 00:30:59.080
I also hate myself

00:30:59.090 --> 00:31:00.590
for not being able to help you.

00:31:01.350 --> 00:31:03.030
I don't have the confidence to compete.

00:31:03.440 --> 00:31:04.680
So I took all the frustration

00:31:05.000 --> 00:31:06.070
out on you.

00:31:07.000 --> 00:31:08.240
I'm always afraid of losing you.

00:31:08.600 --> 00:31:09.830
But in the end, I didn't expect

00:31:10.030 --> 00:31:11.350
I was pushing you further away.

00:31:14.350 --> 00:31:16.110
Maybe I could've done better too.

00:31:17.790 --> 00:31:19.200
If I had told you when he first

00:31:19.310 --> 00:31:20.350
reached out to me,

00:31:20.930 --> 00:31:22.240
would you not have overthought it?

00:31:30.200 --> 00:31:31.400
If I tell you now

00:31:32.350 --> 00:31:33.350
that tonight,

00:31:33.520 --> 00:31:34.720
I spent time alone with a girl,

00:31:34.830 --> 00:31:36.030
but nothing actually happened,

00:31:36.680 --> 00:31:37.640
would you overthink it?

00:31:41.590 --> 00:31:42.510
You'd be suspicious.

00:31:43.270 --> 00:31:44.110
Right?

00:31:44.720 --> 00:31:46.270
Like when I know you met with Lun,

00:31:47.000 --> 00:31:48.440
I'd get suspicious and overthink.

00:31:48.680 --> 00:31:50.550
I even pick irrational fights to provoke you

00:31:53.110 --> 00:31:54.750
just to keep testing how much you love me.

00:32:00.480 --> 00:32:01.320
I admit it.

00:32:02.720 --> 00:32:03.960
There was a moment

00:32:05.640 --> 00:32:06.830
when I really felt tempted.

00:32:13.750 --> 00:32:14.960
What are you trying to say?

00:32:16.110 --> 00:32:17.400
We didn't do anything.

00:32:19.800 --> 00:32:20.770
At that moment, countless

00:32:20.780 --> 00:32:22.440
dirty thoughts flashed through my mind.

00:32:22.830 --> 00:32:23.680
I knew.

00:32:23.750 --> 00:32:25.070
If something had happened,

00:32:25.240 --> 00:32:26.720
I could've ended up losing you.

00:32:26.920 --> 00:32:28.350
I couldn't accept that possibility.

00:32:31.830 --> 00:32:33.110
Like with you and Lun...

00:32:34.400 --> 00:32:35.720
I'm worried you might soften,

00:32:36.440 --> 00:32:38.400
that you'd cling to memories of the past.

00:32:39.480 --> 00:32:40.400
Thinking about how he's

00:32:40.590 --> 00:32:41.640
hurt you all those years...

00:32:41.790 --> 00:32:43.200
Even if you're just hugging

00:32:43.330 --> 00:32:44.200
and saying goodbye

00:32:44.270 --> 00:32:45.750
as friends, I can't accept it.

00:32:46.830 --> 00:32:48.440
But human hearts aren't machines.

00:32:48.920 --> 00:32:51.000
You can't control your thoughts, emotions,

00:32:51.110 --> 00:32:52.030
or feelings.

00:32:52.350 --> 00:32:53.510
I've been too impatient.

00:32:55.070 --> 00:32:56.110
I can't erase him from

00:32:56.110 --> 00:32:57.440
the life you had before.

00:32:59.240 --> 00:33:00.680
I can only do what I can,

00:33:01.640 --> 00:33:02.590
to treat you well.

00:33:11.550 --> 00:33:12.960
That girl...

00:33:14.110 --> 00:33:15.030
She's pretty, right?

00:33:18.310 --> 00:33:19.150
So,

00:33:21.440 --> 00:33:23.070
you… you're mad at me?

00:33:24.790 --> 00:33:26.270
I think she must be very charming.

00:33:27.310 --> 00:33:29.720
Otherwise, why would just
a short time alone with her

00:33:30.720 --> 00:33:32.200
make you seem like a different person?

00:33:35.030 --> 00:33:36.510
You know what you look like right now?

00:33:38.240 --> 00:33:40.200
Like a man who's done something wrong

00:33:40.590 --> 00:33:42.640
showing extra tenderness to his partner.

00:33:46.270 --> 00:33:47.110
I know

00:33:48.960 --> 00:33:50.160
I can't explain it clearly.

00:33:51.750 --> 00:33:52.790
Then don't explain.

00:33:58.030 --> 00:33:59.110
Can we just end this

00:33:59.310 --> 00:34:00.960
pointless argument now?

00:34:04.790 --> 00:34:05.720
You mean,

00:34:07.070 --> 00:34:08.110
you've forgiven me?

00:34:08.730 --> 00:34:10.000
I really want you to know what it

00:34:10.000 --> 00:34:11.210
feels like to be misunderstood.

00:34:12.320 --> 00:34:13.440
But I can't let myself do it.

00:34:14.800 --> 00:34:16.480
I can't treat you the way you treated me.

00:34:24.150 --> 00:34:25.920
So you choose to believe me, right?

00:34:29.030 --> 00:34:29.960
Trust

00:34:30.360 --> 00:34:31.800
shouldn't be a condition for love,

00:34:32.400 --> 00:34:33.240
but its outcome.

00:34:34.280 --> 00:34:35.800
When we love someone,

00:34:35.960 --> 00:34:37.880
we naturally do things to earn their trust.

00:34:48.630 --> 00:34:49.800
- Wait.
- Mm.

00:34:50.840 --> 00:34:51.680
Take off your jacket.

00:34:52.000 --> 00:34:52.840
Mm.

00:34:53.840 --> 00:34:55.110
I can still be jealous, can't I?

00:34:55.380 --> 00:34:57.000
Still wearing the clothes you wore alone

00:34:57.330 --> 00:34:58.190
with another woman.

00:34:58.190 --> 00:34:59.550
Wanna wash it yourself?

00:35:07.670 --> 00:35:09.230
Maybe we should eat first.

00:35:09.800 --> 00:35:11.360
I'm actually a little hungry.

00:35:11.460 --> 00:35:12.390
I'll heat it up for you.

00:35:12.510 --> 00:35:13.840
No need, you...

00:35:13.920 --> 00:35:15.400
Just sit. I'll heat it up.

00:35:17.190 --> 00:35:18.030
Keep talking.

00:35:18.150 --> 00:35:19.630
Don't doze off. Speak.

00:35:19.770 --> 00:35:20.640
Come on.

00:35:20.760 --> 00:35:21.670
No more drinking.

00:35:24.510 --> 00:35:25.440
People, huh.

00:35:26.500 --> 00:35:28.900
(Bei)

00:35:30.510 --> 00:35:32.320
You just finished working, did you?

00:35:32.630 --> 00:35:34.480
You didn't answer my call this afternoon.

00:35:35.190 --> 00:35:36.150
I had things to do.

00:35:36.960 --> 00:35:38.670
Busy now? I wanna ask you something.

00:35:38.840 --> 00:35:40.440
I just got out of the shower.

00:35:41.670 --> 00:35:43.400
But if it's something important,

00:35:43.760 --> 00:35:44.840
I can wait.

00:35:45.630 --> 00:35:46.480
Do you remember

00:35:46.480 --> 00:35:48.060
how long I stayed at your place that day?

00:35:48.880 --> 00:35:49.840
Why are you asking that?

00:35:50.550 --> 00:35:51.550
Your community offers

00:35:51.800 --> 00:35:53.550
free parking for the first half hour.

00:35:53.600 --> 00:35:54.480
But when I left,

00:35:54.500 --> 00:35:55.920
the guard charged me ten yuan.

00:35:56.270 --> 00:35:58.280
The more I thought about it,
the more it bugged me.

00:35:58.880 --> 00:36:00.000
You can't be serious.

00:36:00.280 --> 00:36:01.360
Ten yuan?

00:36:01.590 --> 00:36:03.510
You called me this late just for that?

00:36:04.800 --> 00:36:06.400
Since when did you become so frugal?

00:36:06.910 --> 00:36:07.880
It's not about the money.

00:36:07.960 --> 00:36:10.440
I just don't like being played for a fool.

00:36:10.760 --> 00:36:12.480
I remember when I got to your place,

00:36:12.480 --> 00:36:15.760
it was around 9:52 PM.

00:36:16.360 --> 00:36:18.800
Then I left shortly after.

00:36:18.920 --> 00:36:20.880
I left right as you got a delivery.

00:36:20.900 --> 00:36:21.760
You could check

00:36:21.760 --> 00:36:23.070
the time on that delivery.

00:36:23.400 --> 00:36:24.760
Seriously.

00:36:25.320 --> 00:36:26.160
Wait a sec.

00:36:29.360 --> 00:36:30.200
10:15 PM.

00:36:33.670 --> 00:36:35.000
See? Told you.

00:36:35.670 --> 00:36:37.030
Wasn't even half an hour.

00:36:40.550 --> 00:36:41.800
You're acting weird today.

00:36:43.150 --> 00:36:44.840
Anything else you want to tell me?

00:36:46.630 --> 00:36:47.800
Or maybe,

00:36:48.280 --> 00:36:49.840
about my confession last time,

00:36:50.300 --> 00:36:51.230
you've got a new answer?

00:36:52.480 --> 00:36:53.320
An Miu,

00:36:53.880 --> 00:36:54.840
my answer's

00:36:55.050 --> 00:36:56.190
still the same as that day.

00:36:57.760 --> 00:36:58.670
I have a girlfriend.

00:37:03.360 --> 00:37:04.200
Well, that's boring.

00:37:05.280 --> 00:37:07.070
Then why are you
talking to me so formally?

00:37:07.800 --> 00:37:08.840
Like someone's next to you

00:37:08.840 --> 00:37:10.030
watching you make this call,

00:37:10.150 --> 00:37:11.920
and you're trying
to show loyalty to Xiaoxi.

00:37:12.760 --> 00:37:14.550
Alright then, that's it. Get some rest.

00:37:14.840 --> 00:37:15.680
Hey, wait a sec.

00:37:16.030 --> 00:37:17.880
Isn't this all about that ten yuan?

00:37:18.000 --> 00:37:19.280
I'll transfer you the money.

00:37:20.710 --> 00:37:22.150
Ten yuan for a chat, deal?

00:37:24.480 --> 00:37:26.480
I was planning to call you today anyway.

00:37:27.030 --> 00:37:28.110
I wanted to talk to you,

00:37:28.110 --> 00:37:29.500
but I was worried you might be busy.

00:37:30.190 --> 00:37:31.920
You wanted to talk about Xiaoxi, right?

00:37:32.710 --> 00:37:33.550
Perfect.

00:37:33.800 --> 00:37:34.960
Actually I've got

00:37:35.190 --> 00:37:36.400
something to tell you too.

00:37:38.030 --> 00:37:39.190
Xiaoxi and I

00:37:41.030 --> 00:37:42.000
are going to get married.

00:37:42.110 --> 00:37:42.950
What?

00:37:43.630 --> 00:37:44.590
That fast?

00:37:45.480 --> 00:37:47.480
You could at least congratulate me.

00:37:48.110 --> 00:37:49.230
What I mean is,

00:37:49.670 --> 00:37:51.400
marriage is a lifelong thing.

00:37:52.710 --> 00:37:54.670
Are you sure you've thought it through?

00:37:56.150 --> 00:37:58.440
Do you really know her?

00:37:59.150 --> 00:38:00.280
Do you really know me?

00:38:01.030 --> 00:38:02.030
I've known you for years.

00:38:02.030 --> 00:38:03.280
Do you think I know you or not?

00:38:03.710 --> 00:38:05.030
If you truly knew me,

00:38:05.690 --> 00:38:07.000
you'd know what I'm talking about.

00:38:07.840 --> 00:38:09.880
I think there are things you should know.

00:38:11.360 --> 00:38:12.440
Do you know she's had many…

00:38:12.440 --> 00:38:13.280
An Miu.

00:38:13.800 --> 00:38:15.280
Since I've decided to marry her,

00:38:15.590 --> 00:38:17.000
I accept everything about her.

00:38:17.180 --> 00:38:18.030
Bei...

00:38:18.030 --> 00:38:18.870
Hear me out.

00:38:19.550 --> 00:38:20.440
Believe me.

00:38:21.880 --> 00:38:22.920
I definitely know

00:38:23.670 --> 00:38:24.510
more than you do.

00:38:30.400 --> 00:38:31.480
I accept your money.

00:38:31.970 --> 00:38:32.840
I'll consider it

00:38:32.960 --> 00:38:33.960
an early wedding gift.

00:38:34.320 --> 00:38:36.000
When she and I get married,

00:38:36.280 --> 00:38:37.120
I'll invite you.

00:38:37.170 --> 00:38:38.040
Alright?

00:38:38.070 --> 00:38:38.920
Get some rest.

00:38:52.840 --> 00:38:54.880
Was that a proposal just now?

00:38:57.280 --> 00:38:58.120
Yeah, it was.

00:38:59.360 --> 00:39:00.200
Are you saying yes?

00:39:05.960 --> 00:39:07.000
There's no one else here.

00:39:08.070 --> 00:39:09.070
Be honest with me.

00:39:10.280 --> 00:39:12.110
Everything I told you today...

00:39:13.960 --> 00:39:15.000
You really don't care?

00:39:16.440 --> 00:39:17.280
I don't care.

00:39:17.880 --> 00:39:19.840
But you said Jiang Yifan's a wicked woman.

00:39:20.340 --> 00:39:21.590
I was talking about Jiang Yifan.

00:39:23.070 --> 00:39:24.230
I am Jiang Yifan.

00:39:24.710 --> 00:39:25.550
You're Li Xiaoxi.

00:39:28.150 --> 00:39:29.920
The one I want to marry is

00:39:30.510 --> 00:39:31.510
the Li Xiaoxi I met

00:39:31.920 --> 00:39:33.630
at the bar months ago.

00:39:35.360 --> 00:39:36.200
That's you.

00:39:42.630 --> 00:39:43.590
Silly.

00:39:52.150 --> 00:39:53.000
So...

00:39:54.000 --> 00:39:55.440
Will you marry this silly guy?

00:40:04.760 --> 00:40:06.150
Go on, put it on me.

00:40:19.760 --> 00:40:21.760
Now that it's on,

00:40:22.230 --> 00:40:23.190
no backing out.

00:40:23.400 --> 00:40:24.240
Mm.

00:40:25.440 --> 00:40:26.400
No backing out.

00:40:28.030 --> 00:40:28.920
I won't.

00:40:45.081 --> 00:40:47.680
♪I'll admit♪

00:40:47.681 --> 00:40:51.720
♪My back is faced against the wall♪

00:40:52.601 --> 00:40:56.467
♪There's nothing that
I wouldn't try to do♪

00:40:56.492 --> 00:41:00.680
♪For this feeling to have you♪

00:41:00.961 --> 00:41:03.160
♪I'll resist♪

00:41:03.481 --> 00:41:05.495
♪Your gaze, your lips♪

00:41:05.520 --> 00:41:07.680
♪Your touches again♪

00:41:08.561 --> 00:41:12.541
♪There's no one that
I wouldn't try to fool♪

00:41:12.566 --> 00:41:15.600
♪For an image of you♪

00:41:16.601 --> 00:41:19.040
♪Take my hand again♪

00:41:19.041 --> 00:41:20.800
♪Take my mind again♪

00:41:20.881 --> 00:41:24.240
♪Break into my heart again♪

00:41:24.641 --> 00:41:26.818
♪I'm falling out again♪

00:41:26.843 --> 00:41:28.680
♪I'm on my knees again♪

00:41:28.681 --> 00:41:32.520
♪To beg for the truth♪

00:41:34.361 --> 00:41:38.520
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

00:41:38.521 --> 00:41:43.520
♪Is that the secret to love♪

00:41:43.881 --> 00:41:46.840
♪I thought it had came from
below us♪

00:41:46.921 --> 00:41:50.320
♪Did it come from above♪

00:41:50.401 --> 00:41:54.160
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

00:41:54.401 --> 00:41:59.480
♪Is that the secret to love♪

00:41:59.881 --> 00:42:02.320
♪Is it violent or warming, entrancing♪

00:42:02.321 --> 00:42:06.760
♪This secret of love♪